sequenceDiagram
    participant LS as Lesson/Enrollment Service
    participant RMQ as RabbitMQ
    participant NOT as Notification Service
    participant WS as WebSocket Controller
    participant Student as Frontend (Student Hub)

    Student->>NOT: Establish WebSocket (STOMP) /ws-notifications
    NOT-->>Student: Connected

    LS->>RMQ: Publish Event (e.g. COURSE_PUBLISHED)
    RMQ-->>NOT: Consume Event
    NOT->>NOT: Save Notification to DB
    NOT->>WS: Broadcast Message to /topic/notifications/{userId}
    WS-->>Student: Push Real-time JSON Payload
    Student->>Student: Update Notification Count/Toast
